column16: Pedro Severino flies out to left fielder Eric Thames.
Wilmer Difo grounds into a force out, first baseman Jesus Aguilar to shortstop Orlando Arcia.   Andrew Stevenson to 3rd.    Brian Goodwin out at 2nd.    Wilmer Difo to 1st.
Brian Goodwin walks.   Andrew Stevenson to 2nd.
Andrew Stevenson singles on a line drive to right fielder Domingo Santana.
Jose Lobaton flies out to left fielder Eric Thames.
